---
title: One-Pot Southwest Beef and Cavatappi with Monterey Jack and Baby Spinach
description: This one-and-done dinner in a hurry packs beef, veggies and noodles into one easy bowl. What's even better? It's a meal that everyone is sure to devour!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/casserole-de-boeuf-et-de-cavatappis-a-la-sud-ouest-8a19a385.jpg
